{"tid":1897190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然做唔住結業係好正常，但希望大家可以俾黃店一個機會","createTime":"2020-02-25T14:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T12:35:22.000Z","uid":163704,"like":39,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"236f321c46546dff4fe374780aba1e6bd92151a9","tid":1897190,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"我地知道結業背後總有一個原因，而當中有部分原因喺改變唔到。我地搵咗唔少黃店老闆同有唔同背景義工一齊諗方法去幫助喺困境嘅黃店。<br />\n<br />\n已知即將結業黃店名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://factvote.com/projects/即將結業黃店\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffactvote.com%2Fprojects%2F%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=829bbedc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://factvote.com/projects/即將結業黃店</a><br />\n<br />\n為了減少即將結業黃店的出現，我們需要大家的幫助。如果你知道某一間黃店面臨結業的危機，請填寫以下google form。(需於 <a href=\"http://www.factvote.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.factvote.com&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=480a06ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.factvote.com</a> 內創建該店，或可先於站內搜尋該店 。)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/28y8vav4gcGrNsxb9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F28y8vav4gcGrNsxb9&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=d659d022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/28y8vav4gcGrNsxb9</a><br />\n<br />\n我地收集資料後，大家可以去下面條link搵黃店支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://factvote.com/projects/黃店結業告急\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffactvote.com%2Fprojects%2F%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E5%91%8A%E6%80%A5&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=16bbb7fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://factvote.com/projects/黃店結業告急</a><br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣參與義工，可以聯絡我地。<br />\nFacebook:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FactVote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFactVote&d=JcMWRxryG4